General.Name: Fibre-Crown Manufacturing Inc
General.Description: Fibre-Crown Manufacturing Inc. does not have significant operations. The company intends to identify and evaluate assets or businesses with a view to completing a qualifying transaction. Previously, it was involved in developing and manufacturing architectural details, claddings, and moldings. Fibre-Crown Manufacturing Inc. incorporated in 2000 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
